        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/news/future-of-jet-secured-with-new-european-contract">Future of JET secured with new European contract</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>The future of the world’s largest operational fusion research facility has been secured with a new contract signed between the UK and the European Commission.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>


