    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2019-01-25">25 January 2019</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>News story</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/news/fusion-an-example-of-government-science-ambitions-says-minister">Fusion an example of Government science ambitions, says Minister</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>New Minister of State for Universities, Science, Research and Innovation Chris Skidmore gave his first major speech on science policy during a visit to UKAEA.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

        </div>
        <div class="column-one-third">
