        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/news/duke-of-cambridge-unveils-the-uks-new-fusion-project-at-culham">Duke of Cambridge unveils the UK's new fusion project at Culham</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>The Duke was at Culham to mark the end of construction of the UK’s new nuclear fusion experiment, MAST Upgrade.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>

