              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/news/new-training-centre-to-keep-oxfordshire-a-hi-tech-hotspot">New training centre to keep Oxfordshire a hi-tech hotspot</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>A training centre that will equip up to 350 apprentices per year with badly-needed technical skills for the local economy is now taking shape at Culham Science Centre near Abingdon.</p>
</div></div>


